<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Meme Page</title>
    <style>
        body, html {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: white;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        /* Full screen section for the meme */
        .meme-container {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #000;
        }

        .meme-container img {
            max-width: 90%;
            max-height: 80vh;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        /* Section for the text box */
        .text-section {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 40px;
        }

        .text-box {
            background: #1e1e1e;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 90%;
            border: 1px solid #333;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .scroll-hint {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.6;
            animation: bounce 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% {transform: translateY(0);}
            40% {transform: translateY(-10px);}
            60% {transform: translateY(-5px);}
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="meme-container">
        <img src="https://i.chzbgr.com/full/10507669760/h340C8660/rich-friend-somebody-calls-him-rich-d" alt="Funny Meme">
        <div class="scroll-hint">Scroll down for the secret text ↓</div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-section">
        <div class="text-box">
            <h3>The Message</h3>
            <p>
                Campus ka ek legendary room, jahan poker ki tables lagti hain, nashe ki philosophy chalti hai
                Itni activities hoti hain wahan ki Rekha Rani ne bhi kai baar raid maar ke sabko pakda hai.
                Senior boys ke liye yeh sirf ek room nahi… ultimate kalesh zone hai.
                Agar itni iconic jagah yaad aa gayi ho, toh jaake action team ki room check karo…
                Ho sakta hai iss baar daaru nahi, next clue tumhara wait kar raha ho.

            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
